рҹҢҚ рқ—ӣрқ—јрқҳ„ рқҳҒрқ—ј рқ—”рқ—°рқ—өрқ—¶рқ—Ірқҳғрқ—І рқ—ҹрқ—јрқ—°рқ—®рқ—№рқ—¶рқҳҖрқ—®рқҳҒрқ—¶рқ—јрқ—» рқ—¶рқ—» рқ—Ҙрқ—Ірқ—®рқ—°рқҳҒ.рқ—·рқҳҖ (Step by Step)

Your React app works perfectly вҖ” in one language.
The moment you go global? Everything breaks. рҹҳ¶

Here's the complete step-by-step localisation setup рҹ‘Ү

---

рҹ§  **рқ—Әрқ—өрқ—®рқҳҒ рқ—Әрқ—І'рқ—ҝрқ—І рқ—•рқҳӮрқ—¶рқ—№рқ—ұрқ—¶рқ—»рқ—ҙ**

рҹ‘ү Multi-language React app
рҹ‘ү Auto language detection
рҹ‘ү Dynamic language switching
рҹ‘ү Formatted dates, numbers & currencies

```plaintext
English вҶ’ French вҶ’ Japanese вҶ’ Arabic (RTL)
All from one codebase. Zero rewrites.
```

---

рҹ“Ұ 1пёҸвғЈ **рқ—ңрқ—»рқҳҖрқҳҒрқ—®рқ—№рқ—№ рқ——рқ—Ірқ—Ҫрқ—Ірқ—»рқ—ұрқ—Ірқ—»рқ—°рқ—¶рқ—ІрқҳҖ**

```bash
npm install i18next react-i18next
npm install i18next-browser-languagedetector
npm install i18next-http-backend
```

вң” `i18next` вҖ” core translation engine
вң” `react-i18next` вҖ” React bindings & hooks
вң” `browser-languagedetector` вҖ” auto detects user's language
вң” `http-backend` вҖ” lazy loads translation files

---

рҹ—ӮпёҸ 2пёҸвғЈ **рқ—ҷрқ—јрқ—№рқ—ұрқ—Ірқ—ҝ рқ—ҰрқҳҒрқ—ҝрқҳӮрқ—°рқҳҒрқҳӮрқ—ҝрқ—І**

рҹ‘ү Keep translations outside your components

```plaintext
src/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ i18n/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ index.js          вҶҗ i18n config
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ locales/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ en/
в”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ translation.json
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ fr/
в”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ translation.json
в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ ja/
в”Ӯ           в””в”Җв”Җ translation.json
```

вң” One folder per language
вң” Same key structure across all files
вң” Easy to hand off to translators

---

рҹ“қ 3пёҸвғЈ **рқ—–рқ—ҝрқ—Ірқ—®рқҳҒрқ—І рқ—§рқ—ҝрқ—®рқ—»рқҳҖрқ—№рқ—®рқҳҒрқ—¶рқ—јрқ—» рқ—ҷрқ—¶рқ—№рқ—ІрқҳҖ**

рҹ‘ү Same keys, different values per language

```json
// locales/en/translation.json
{
  "welcome": "Welcome, {{name}}!",
  "logout": "Logout",
  "items_one": "{{count}} item",
  "items_other": "{{count}} items",
  "errors": {
    "required": "This field is required"
  }
}

// locales/fr/translation.json
{
  "welcome": "Bienvenue, {{name}}!",
  "logout": "Se dГ©connecter",
  "items_one": "{{count}} article",
  "items_other": "{{count}} articles",
  "errors": {
    "required": "Ce champ est obligatoire"
  }
}
```

вң” Use nested keys for grouping
вң” `{{variable}}` syntax for dynamic values
вң” `_one` / `_other` suffix for plurals

---

вҡҷпёҸ 4пёҸвғЈ **рқ—–рқ—јрқ—»рқ—ірқ—¶рқ—ҙрқҳӮрқ—ҝрқ—І рқ—¶рқҹӯрқҹҙрқ—»**

```js
// src/i18n/index.js
import i18n from 'i18next';
import { initReactI18next } from 'react-i18next';
import LanguageDetector from 'i18next-browser-languagedetector';
import HttpBackend from 'i18next-http-backend';

i18n
  .use(HttpBackend)
  .use(LanguageDetector)
  .use(initReactI18next)
  .init({
    fallbackLng: 'en',       // default if language not found
    debug: false,

    detection: {
      order: ['localStorage', 'navigator'],
      cacheUserLanguage: true  // remembers user choice
    },

    backend: {
      loadPath: '/locales/{{lng}}/translation.json'
    },

    interpolation: {
      escapeValue: false       // React handles XSS
    }
  });

export default i18n;
```

вң” `fallbackLng` вҖ” safety net if translation key missing
вң” `cacheUserLanguage` вҖ” persists language in localStorage
вң” `loadPath` вҖ” lazy loads only needed language file

---

рҹҡҖ 5пёҸвғЈ **рқ—–рқ—јрқ—»рқ—»рқ—Ірқ—°рқҳҒ рқҳҒрқ—ј рқ—Ҙрқ—Ірқ—®рқ—°рқҳҒ рқ—”рқ—Ҫрқ—Ҫ**

```jsx
// src/main.jsx
import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import App from './App';
import './i18n/index.js';   // вҶҗ import before App renders

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))
  .render(<App />);
```

вң” Import i18n before App renders
вң” No Provider needed вҖ” i18next is global
вң” Translations load automatically on mount

---

рҹ”Ө 6пёҸвғЈ **рқ—ЁрқҳҖрқ—І рқ—§рқ—ҝрқ—®рқ—»рқҳҖрқ—№рқ—®рқҳҒрқ—¶рқ—јрқ—»рқҳҖ рқ—¶рқ—» рқ—–рқ—јрқ—әрқ—Ҫрқ—јрқ—»рқ—Ірқ—»рқҳҒрқҳҖ**

```jsx
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next';

function Dashboard() {
  const { t } = useTranslation();

  return (
    <div>
      {/* Basic translation */}
      <h1>{t('welcome', { name: 'John' })}</h1>

      {/* Nested key */}
      <span>{t('errors.required')}</span>

      {/* Pluralisation вҖ” auto picks _one or _other */}
      <p>{t('items', { count: 5 })}</p>
    </div>
  );
}
```

вң” `t('key')` вҖ” translate a string
вң” `t('key', { var })` вҖ” with dynamic values
вң” `t('key', { count })` вҖ” automatic pluralisation

---

рҹҢҗ 7пёҸвғЈ **рқ—ҹрқ—®рқ—»рқ—ҙрқҳӮрқ—®рқ—ҙрқ—І рқ—Ұрқҳ„рқ—¶рқҳҒрқ—°рқ—өрқ—Ірқ—ҝ рқ—–рқ—јрқ—әрқ—Ҫрқ—јрқ—»рқ—Ірқ—»рқҳҒ**

```jsx
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next';

const languages = [
  { code: 'en', label: 'English' },
  { code: 'fr', label: 'FranГ§ais' },
  { code: 'ja', label: 'ж—Ҙжң¬иӘһ' },
  { code: 'ar', label: 'Ш§Щ„Ш№ШұШЁЩҠШ©' }
];

function LanguageSwitcher() {
  const { i18n } = useTranslation();

  const changeLanguage = (code) => {
    i18n.changeLanguage(code);

    // Handle RTL languages
    document.dir = code === 'ar' ? 'rtl' : 'ltr';
  };

  return (
    <div>
      {languages.map(({ code, label }) => (
        <button
          key={code}
          onClick={() => changeLanguage(code)}
          className={i18n.language === code ? 'active' : ''}
        >
          {label}
        </button>
      ))}
    </div>
  );
}
```

вң” `i18n.changeLanguage()` вҖ” switches instantly
вң” `document.dir = 'rtl'` вҖ” flips layout for Arabic
вң” Language saved in localStorage automatically

---

рҹ“… 8пёҸвғЈ **рқ——рқ—®рқҳҒрқ—ІрқҳҖ, рқ—ЎрқҳӮрқ—әрқ—Ҝрқ—Ірқ—ҝрқҳҖ & рқ—–рқҳӮрқ—ҝрқ—ҝрқ—Ірқ—»рқ—°рқҳҶ**

```jsx
function PriceDisplay({ amount, date }) {
  const { i18n } = useTranslation();
  const locale = i18n.language;

  // Format currency
  const price = new Intl.NumberFormat(locale, {
    style: 'currency',
    currency: locale === 'ja' ? 'JPY' : 'USD'
  }).format(amount);

  // Format date
  const formattedDate = new Intl.DateTimeFormat(locale, {
    year: 'numeric',
    month: 'long',
    day: 'numeric'
  }).format(date);

  return (
    <div>
      <p>{price}</p>
      <p>{formattedDate}</p>
    </div>
  );
}
```

вң” Always use `Intl` API вҖ” never manual formatting
вң” Currency code changes per locale
вң” Date format adapts automatically

---

вҸі 9пёҸвғЈ **рқ—ӣрқ—®рқ—»рқ—ұрқ—№рқ—¶рқ—»рқ—ҙ рқ—ҹрқ—јрқ—®рқ—ұрқ—¶рқ—»рқ—ҙ рқ—ҰрқҳҒрқ—®рқҳҒрқ—І**

рҹ‘ү Translations load async вҖ” handle the loading state

```jsx
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next';
import { Suspense } from 'react';

// Wrap app in Suspense
function App() {
  return (
    <Suspense fallback={<div>Loading...</div>}>
      <Dashboard />
    </Suspense>
  );
}

// Or check inside component
function Dashboard() {
  const { t, ready } = useTranslation();

  if (!ready) return <Spinner />;

  return <h1>{t('welcome')}</h1>;
}
```

вң” `ready` вҖ” true when translations are loaded
вң” `Suspense` вҖ” cleaner loading handling at app level
вң” Never render untranslated content to users

---

рҹҡЁ **рқ—–рқ—јрқ—әрқ—әрқ—јрқ—» рқ— рқ—¶рқҳҖрқҳҒрқ—®рқ—ёрқ—ІрқҳҖ**

вқҢ Hardcoding strings inside JSX
вқҢ Not handling RTL layout for Arabic/Hebrew
вқҢ Using English keys as translation keys `t('Welcome back!')`
вқҢ Formatting dates manually instead of `Intl` API
вқҢ Bundling all language files вҖ” lazy load instead
вқҢ Adding i18n after the app is built вҖ” costs 10x more

---

рҹ’Ў **рқ—Ұрқ—Ірқ—»рқ—¶рқ—јрқ—ҝ-рқ—ҹрқ—Ірқҳғрқ—Ірқ—№ рқ—ңрқ—»рқҳҖрқ—¶рқ—ҙрқ—өрқҳҒ**

Translation is 10% of localisation. Dates, RTL, plurals, and culture are the other 90%.
Build the infrastructure on day one вҖ” adding it later is a full rewrite.

---

рҹҺҜ **рқ—ңрқ—»рқҳҒрқ—Ірқ—ҝрқҳғрқ—¶рқ—Ірқҳ„ рқ—ўрқ—»рқ—І-рқ—ҹрқ—¶рқ—»рқ—Ірқ—ҝ**

Localisation in React is achieved using react-i18next for translation management, the browser LanguageDetector for auto-detection, the Intl API for dates, numbers and currencies, and dynamic RTL switching via document.dir вҖ” all configured once and consumed anywhere via the useTranslation hook.

